OL,3,CFamily launches fundraiser for Swiss
OL,4,CAlps rescuers who tried to save man's
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FThe family of a "beloved" Scot who
OL,8,Fdied climbing a Swiss mountain has
OL,9,Flaunched a fundraiser to help the
OL,10,Frescue team that tried to save his
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FAndy McGlinn, 50, died on Mount Rigi
OL,14,Fin central Switzerland on Sunday. The
OL,15,FAlps mountain is known as the Queen of
OL,16,Fthe Mountains and is surrounded by
OL,17,FLake Lucerne, Lake Zug, and Lake
OL,18,FLauerz.
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@YO]
