OL,3,CFamily launches fundraiser for Swiss
OL,4,CAlps rescuers who tried to save man's
OL,5,Clife
OL,7,FMr McGlinn's family has since launched
OL,8,Fa GoFundMe to raise funds for Rega,
OL,9,Fthe Swiss air-rescue service.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FIn a statement posted on GoFundMe, the
OL,17,Ffamily wrote: "Our beloved Andy
OL,18,FMcGlinn, only 50 years old, passed
OL,19,Faway suddenly last Sunday while doing
OL,20,Fwhat he loved on the Rigi.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
